+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${FULLPKGNAME} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

PAK-files from the original Dune 2 are needed to play Dune Legacy.  Data
files and music files should be placed in ${PREFIX}/share/dunelegacy/ or
~/.config/dunelegacy/data/.
